here's a simple way to do what you want:

[code:e1es95q8]&lt;object name=&quot;player&quot;&gt;
  &lt;inherit name=&quot;editor_object&quot; /&gt;
  &lt;inherit name=&quot;editor_player&quot; /&gt;
